{
  "stem": "21978.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And after the work, when the lorry took the corpses to the crematoria to be burned, we came to the barrack.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we didn't have any change of clothing, no overalls.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We washed our hands.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There was not a shower, nowhere for the baths.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Every time when I have a hot shower with nice soap, I remember this location that we had to wash our hands with ice cold water.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Instead of soap, we had some kind of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] chemical which is used now in swimming pools, I think, something very strong.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We washed with that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And then we have been given a reward.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The reward of extra portion of soup or maybe extra portion of bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Now you don't think that you could eat after work like that, but we did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We had to, because we wanted to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was a urge to survive from minute to minute, from day to day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we did it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we have been more or less like robots doing this kind of work, looking after the dying.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We have seen so many dying and handled so many dead ones, I can't count anymore.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "For me, at that time, it was just a work which we had to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we had to push our emotions back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "It was not a question of thinking-- this must have been a girl who might have looked nice, nothing like that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We just couldn't think.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We just had to be robots.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "That might have been a way of surviving.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Because if we would sit down and cried, we would have collapsed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "That might have been the way that we could do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A long, long building, which was originally stable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were horses kept.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
